---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | bbrep">
  <section class="shell content prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Public program reputation</h1>
    <p>
      bbrep is a public repository of bug bounty and VDP reputation, based on
      reviews from researchers in the community.
    </p>
    <p>
      The goal is simple: make program quality easier to see, and help researchers
      avoid wasting time on programs that do not value their work.
    </p>
    <p>
      Only public, disclosure-safe information belongs here. No private report
      details, bounty IDs, payloads, or confidential conversations.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
